dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Topatopa Mountains quadrangle, Ventura County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "First printing, December 1996." "T.W. Dibblee, Jr., field work, 1946,1980". "Prepared in cooperation with the U.S. Forest Service, Los Padres National Forest; California Department of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; and U.S. Geological Survey." Includes 2 col. cross sections, acknowledgements, index to sources of geology, age correlation chart and location map. Includes bibliography.
dc_creator_sm: Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. Geological Foundation
